snippet.title: The Witch and the Hundred Knight 2 - Character Trailer (PS4)
snippet.description:
Pre-order today @ http://bit.ly/Witch100Knight2
Learn more @ http://WitchHundred2.com

The Hundred Knight has a lot to overcome as it helps Amalie and Chelka in The Witch and the Hundred Knight 2. Meet the dynamic cast in this trailer featuring many faces that you will come to know soon!

Keep up with all of the latest info by following us on Facebook (/NISAmericaInc) and on Twitter (@NISAmerica). Visit http://nisamerica.com/ to learn more.
